      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALIMONIE (9) could only manage third last start over 1800m at this track, beaten 14 metres, after victory at the previous appearance over 1800m at this track. Beautifully placed and is sure to play a major role. REACT TO BEAUTY (7) worked to find the lead but couldn't keep going and finished a close fourth last start over 1800m at this track. Tactics will be crucial from this wide draw. Meets a similar line up and he can figure in the finish. BOHEMIAN BRAIDS (6) should be at his peak for this. Finished second over 1800m at this track at the latest appearance a week ago. Sure to give the top fancies plenty to think about. TWIN CONNECTION (5) is worth another chance after a last-start ninth over 1800m at this track nine days ago.",
